## Start 14-day Trial
Simplify Customer Support with Our Helpdesk

### Communication from Live Chats and Messengers in One Place
Consolidate all client messages from various messengers and your website widget into a single, organised hub.

### Distributing Tickets between Agents, Depending on Their Workload
Set criteria to distribute tickets among assignees based on their workload.

### Automatic Actions (Triggers) for Tickets
Automate key actions to streamline your workflow and work more quickly and efficiently.

### Automatic Actions (Triggers) for Chats
Enhance your control and automate actions within chat interactions.

### Knowledge Base
Create a centralised corporate wiki packed with invaluable information about your products and services.

### Client Portal
This web-based platform offers customers an easy and independent ticketing experience.

### Open API and Integrations
* Active Directory: Access to Pulsedesk can be managed via Azure Active Directory.
* Bitrix24: Connect Bitrix24 to access all the information available about a customer with just one click.
* Jira: Integration allows you to track tasks directly in Pulsedesk.
* Zapier: Zapier is a service that facilitates the Pulsedesk integration with over 5000 apps.

